程序包 org.janusgraph.core.attribute

枚举 Text

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Text>
org.janusgraph.core.attribute.Text
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Comparable<Text>, java.lang.constant.Constable, BiPredicate<Object,​Object>, JanusGraphPredicate
public enum Text
extends Enum<Text>
implements JanusGraphPredicate
Comparison relations for text objects. These comparisons are based on a tokenized representation of the text, i.e. the text is considered as a set of word tokens.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)

    CONTAINS

    Whether the text contains a token is at X Levenshtein of a token (case insensitive) with X=: - 0 for strings of one or two characters - 1 for strings of three, four or five characters - 2 for strings of more than five characters
